CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: HUHUTECH International, through its subsidiaries, specializes in providing factory facility management and monitoring systems, including high-purity process system and factory management and control systems for its industrial clients, who are mainly semi-conductor manufacturers and electronics manufacturers in China. Its products and services are widely used by semi-conductor manufacturers, LED and micro-electronics factories, as well as some pharmaceutical, food and beverage manufacturers.
